#string STR_MRC_SAFEMODEOVERRIDE_PROMPT         #language en-US "MRC Safe Mode Override"
#string STR_MRC_SAFEMODEOVERRIDE_HELP           #language en-US "Bit mask to enable the use of the input safe mode values"
                                                When a bit is set, the corresponding safe mode input field value will be used instead of the pre-defined MRC safe mode configuration.
                                                The definitions are: [0] Enable DdrSafeMode override, [1] Enable McSafeMode override, [2] Reserved,
